<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV18">
<l>viṭattavāyo rāyirami rāyiramkaṇ ventaḻal</l>
<l>viṭuttuvīḻvi lātapōka mikkacōti tokkacīr</l>
<l>toṭuttumēlvi tāṉamāya pauvanīra rāvaṇaip</l>
<l>paṭuttapāyaṟ paḷḷikoḷva teṉkolvēlai vaṇṇaṇē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O ocean-hued [Lord]! What is this sleeping on the bedding</l>
<l>that is the serpent-bed spread out on the ocean water,</l>
<l>[whose hoods] are a canopy above whose enjoyability never falls,</l>
<l>Who has abundant light and gathered beauty</l>
<l rend="indent">—[a serpent] that emits hot fire from a thousand poison[-filled] mouths</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] two thousand eyes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
